{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 67,
  "title": "第六十七章（三寶）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下皆謂我道大，似不肖。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯大，故似不肖，"
    },
    {
      "text": "若肖久矣。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其細也夫。"
    },
    {
      "text": "我有三寶，持而保之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "一曰慈，"
    },
    {
      "text": "二曰儉，"
    },
    {
      "text": "三曰不敢為天下先。"
    },
    {
      "text": "慈故能勇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "儉故能廣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不敢為天下先，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故能成器長。"
    },
    {
      "text": "今舍慈且勇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "舍儉且廣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "舍後且先，"
    },
    {
      "text": "死矣！"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫慈以戰則勝，以守則固。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天將救之，以慈衛之。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：天下謂我德大，我則佯愚似不肖。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯獨名德大者為身害，故佯愚似若不肖。無所分別，無所割截，不賤人而自責。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "肖，善也。謂辨惠也。若大辨惠之人，身高自貴行察察之政所從來久矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言辨惠者唯如小人，非長者。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "老子言：我有三寶，抱持而保倚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "愛百姓若赤子。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "賦歛若取之於己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "執謙退，不為倡始也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以慈仁，故能勇於忠孝也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天子身能節儉，故民日用廣矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不為天下首先。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "成器長，謂得道人也。我能為得道人之長也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "今世人舍慈仁，但為勇武。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "舍其儉約，但為奢泰。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "舍其後己，但為人先。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "所行如此，動入死地。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫慈仁者，百姓親附，并心一意，故以戰則勝敵，以守衛則堅固。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天將救助善人，必與慈仁之性，使能自營助也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
